1
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:34,950
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:39,460
[2020]

3
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,120
Come on, everyone, take a look

4
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:39,150
at the sales performance
for the last 3 months.

5
00:01:39,150 --> 00:01:40,759
Liu Yun is ranked first.

6
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,200
Li Xiaohong is second.

7
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,120
He Cong is third.

8
00:01:44,750 --> 00:01:46,550
-Xia Xiaolan, you...
-Ms. Qian.

9
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,570
I have something to ask Ms. Liu.

10
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:51,240
Ms. Liu, I would like to ask,

11
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,759
why before every meeting,

12
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,479
you'd assign me temporary tasks,

13
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:55,280
using small accounts

14
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,610
to fill up my work hours.

15
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,280
In the end,
the clients I bring to sign deals

16
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,509
become your performance figures—

17
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:00,590
may I ask why?

18
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,790
Xiaolan,

19
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,700
is there a misunderstanding?

20
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,610
Calm down first.

21
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,210
Let's talk privately.

22
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,240
No need.

23
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,450
Let's say it now.

24
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:13,670
I hate green tea.

25
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:18,230
[Episode 5:
A Villain Shouldn't Talk Too Much]

26
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,840
You're right.

27
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,030
But in the future,

28
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,430
more and more people

29
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:22,910
will be willing to pay

30
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:24,310
for these fancy clothes.

31
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,440
This is a business opportunity for us.

32
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,470
You can predict the future?

33
00:02:33,430 --> 00:02:35,630
Then what do you want to switch lines to?

34
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,940
I want to switch lines to butchering pigs.

35
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:39,310
I have martial arts skills.

36
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:41,110
So butchering is easy to pick up.

37
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:46,680
Have you thought about
going to the special economic zone

38
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,480
to take a look?

39
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,430
You mean
the Shengcheng Special Economic Zone?

40
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:52,020
You need a Border Permit to go there.

41
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:54,360
But it's all just
construction sites there.

42
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,490
It's a mess.

43
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,590
If I go there,

44
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,030
what business could I do?

45
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,430
Go take a look if you get the chance.

46
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:00,470
Maybe you'll really find

47
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,200
some business opportunities.

48
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:03,190
Okay.

49
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,560
I'll go take a look when I have time.

50
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,280
So when will you

51
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,400
come back again to Longcheng?

52
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,870
We'll meet again
when fate brings us together.

53
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,400
I'm heading to the station.

54
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,240
You can check in these goods.

55
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,600
You didn't know, right?

56
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,840
I know the train station well.

57
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,640
I'll take you.

58
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,680
Please watch my stall for a bit.

59
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,710
I'll be right back.

60
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:20,520
Really, no need.

61
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,310
I can go by myself.

62
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,190
No need.

63
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,770
Let me take it.

64
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:26,490
Buy some other things too.

65
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,250
Take a look.

66
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,710
Oh my.

67
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,760
People outside these days

68
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,220
dress like this?

69
00:03:36,829 --> 00:03:38,680
They wear such stylish clothes.

70
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,560
Look how colorful they are.

71
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,000
-This one.
-Auntie.

72
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,200
You look good in this.

73
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,420
This color suits you well.

74
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,190
Isn't this too youthful for me?

75
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:48,990
It looks good.

76
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:49,590
Well...

77
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,079
-Xiaolan is back.
-Does it suit me?

78
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:51,520
Mom.

79
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:52,750
Why didn't you send a telegram?

80
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:53,860
I would have picked you up.

81
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:55,590
No need. I just carried it back.

82
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,190
Look, Xiaolan brought back

83
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,310
such colorful clothes.

84
00:03:58,310 --> 00:03:58,910
Look.

85
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,520
Well...

86
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,000
This is so much stock.

87
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,360
You spent all the money you brought?

88
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,680
Of course.

89
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,960
It's rare that I get to go there.

90
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,620
It'd be a waste not to stock up.

91
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:12,070
Look at this.

92
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:16,630
Look at this little button.

93
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:17,040
Yeah.

94
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,240
It really is nice.

95
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,050
Where are we going to sell all this?

96
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,490
There is a place.

97
00:04:28,010 --> 00:04:28,950
Look at this.

98
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,080
There's more here.

99
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,000
Xiaolan.

100
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,120
Working in these shoes

101
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,390
is too uncomfortable.

102
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:40,310
Mom, trust me.

103
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:41,640
It looks good like this.

104
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,630
Does it look good?

105
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,840
Then this sweater...

106
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,310
Hang it over there.

107
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,150
Don't miss out!

108
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:53,630
Goods from Longcheng!

109
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,000
Come take a look!

110
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:56,750
Xiaolan.

111
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:58,920
Why does everything end in 9.9?

112
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,360
This 19.9

113
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,040
is only a dime less than 20.

114
00:05:02,090 --> 00:05:02,820
But that 1 dime

115
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,200
makes it much more tempting.

116
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:04,680
Get it?

117
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:08,830
Miss.

118
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,220
Look at these jeans.

119
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,240
-They're from Longcheng.
-Xiaoqin!

120
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:12,750
Come on.

121
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,830
New arrivals today.

122
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:15,160
Come again!

123
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,430
Xiaolan.

124
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:19,330
There are many buyers,

125
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,800
but there are many sellers too.

126
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,270
Mom.

127
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,560
Our target customers

128
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,390
aren't factory girls,

129
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,810
but office workers.

130
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,600
They...

131
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,360
not only care about style,

132
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,160
but also have aesthetic demands.

133
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:31,800
Look.

134
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,040
Over there is the City Hall.

135
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,390
Here is the farmers' market.

136
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,830
Past this is the Department Store.

137
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,920
So on their commute,

138
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:41,310
[City Hall] [Farmers' Market] [Us] [Department Store]

139
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,040
they have to pass by here.

140
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,560
Right?

141
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,400
I have an idea.

142
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,750
Mom, Mom.

143
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,560
Put this on.

144
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,560
Me?

145
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,950
No way. It's too gaudy. I...

146
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,310
Mom, do you trust me?

147
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,010
I trust you, but...

148
00:05:56,020 --> 00:05:56,750
Listen to me.

149
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,950
Put this on.

150
00:05:58,310 --> 00:05:59,120
Just go to the places I mentioned

151
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,320
and walk around a bit.

152
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,160
Xiaolan...

153
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,310
Well... Well...

154
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,640
-What's this for?
-Mom.

155
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,630
Be confident.

156
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,400
Confidence makes you shine.

157
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,000
Okay.

158
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,250
I'll listen to you.

159
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,360
How much for this one?

160
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:13,600
The price is marked.

161
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,920
9.9 each.

162
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,800
9.9?

163
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,800
Let me think about it.

164
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,800
Sure, no problem.

165
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,200
Come back again.

166
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:20,720
Okay.

167
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,120
Xiaolan!

168
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,000
Xiaolan!

169
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,270
I hadn't even

170
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:30,830
reached the Department Store

171
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,510
and a few young people
already surrounded me,

172
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,750
asking where I bought this shirt

173
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,800
and pants.

174
00:06:35,010 --> 00:06:36,430
I got scared and ran right back.

175
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,040
Mom, Mom.

176
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,120
Don't be nervous.

177
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,600
Is it over there?

178
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:40,600
It should be.

179
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,270
Quick, quick.

180
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,070
Here comes business.

181
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,040
Go sit down. Go sit down.

182
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,680
What business?

183
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,070
Let me hang this sign up in the meantime.

184
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:45,560
Sis.

185
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:47,270
Did you buy your clothes here?

186
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:47,840
I... yes.

187
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,510
Yes, yes.

188
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,040
Right here in our shop.

189
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,920
This outfit looks great.

190
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,990
Take a look. Come take a look.

191
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:52,350
They're all from Longcheng.

192
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:53,600
How much is this knit top?

193
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,630
You have a great eye.

194
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:56,000
These are the latest stocks I brought in

195
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,930
from Longcheng.

196
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,360
Prices are labeled.

197
00:06:58,430 --> 00:06:59,950
The ad says 29.90.

198
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,800
The clothes are nice,

199
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,040
but a bit expensive.

200
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,390
Just one sweater

201
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,480
costs a month's salary.

202
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,360
But you have to look at

203
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,360
its material.

204
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,000
Look.

205
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,830
These are precision machine-knitted.

206
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,560
Look how even the stitching is.

207
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,310
You can't get this quality by hand.

208
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:14,240
In Longcheng, these goods

209
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:14,870
are all for export

210
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:15,830
to foreign countries.

211
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:17,600
It's still a bit too expensive.

212
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,050
It's not expensive.

213
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:20,560
Our prices are clearly marked.

214
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,600
You don't need to worry others

215
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,830
are paying less than you.

216
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,290
The quality is excellent.

217
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,240
Your viscount for buying a set,

218
00:07:26,260 --> 00:07:27,110
what does that mean?

219
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:30,300
[Discount]

220
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,920
It's not viscount but discount.

221
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,790
It means

222
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,720
if you buy the top and pants

223
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,390
together,

224
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,310
you get 10% off.

225
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,040
The top is 2.90 cheaper,

226
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,470
and same goes for the pants.

227
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,090
I know.

228
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,310
That's how they do it

229
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,430
in Gangdao movies.

230
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,000
Yes, yes.

231
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,950
You're so stylish.

232
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,120
Exactly, that's it.

233
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:44,120
All right, give me a set then.

234
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,190
And help me pick a pair of pants.

235
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,270
Sure, let me pick you one.

236
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:47,870
These two are different colors,

237
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:48,800
but both look great.

238
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,520
Look at the cut.

239
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,390
Bell-bottoms. You'll look slim in them.

240
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,430
If I

241
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,390
buy with someone else,

242
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:55,270
do we get the discount?

243
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,190
Of course!

244
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,310
You're so smart.

245
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,570
No problem. Of course.

246
00:07:58,750 --> 00:07:59,270
These pants.

247
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,190
Feel free to look around.

248
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:00,720
Xiaolan.

249
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,750
Of course.

250
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,720
Take a look.

251
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,000
Well, how about...

252
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,700
I go take another walk around?

253
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:07,830
Sure, Mom.

254
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:09,120
Be confident.

255
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:11,220
This one looks good too.

256
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:12,430
-Come.
-Let's buy them together.

257
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:13,510
You want both?

258
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,310
I'll wrap it up for you.

259
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,800
-It'll be...
-That'll be...

260
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,360
45.

261
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,430
That's the discounted price.

262
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,630
Don't miss out!

263
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:22,390
10% off for sets!

264
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,190
45.

265
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:23,720
Okay.

266
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,880
Let me bag it for you.

267
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,220
It's so beautiful.

268
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,549
90, 95, 500.

269
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:37,870
1, 2, 3, 4, 5.

270
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,240
505.40 yuan.

271
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,320
We sold
less than half the stock this time,

272
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:43,720
but we've already made back

273
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,550
505.40 yuan.

274
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,030
Look at our Xiaolan.

275
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:47,870
How is she so good at making money?

276
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,440
Auntie,

277
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:50,050
I don't want to split

278
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,240
the profit we made this time yet.

279
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,240
This way, we can

280
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,550
buy more stock next time.

281
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:54,290
No problem.

282
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,380
I'll listen to you.

283
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,960
We're not in a rush
to use the money anyway.

284
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,630
Making money is definitely a good thing,

285
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,960
but it can't interfere with your studies.

286
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:03,910
Yeah.

287
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,930
Why aren't the results out yet?

288
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:08,130
How about this?

289
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:09,550
I'll go to No.1 High School tomorrow

290
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,550
and ask Chen Qing.

291
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:12,440
You two just focus on the stall,

292
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:12,910
okay?

293
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,710
-Sure.
-Sure.

294
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,480
Mom,

295
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,440
you keep this money for now.

296
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,280
It looks like

297
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,550
we'll have to go to the bank

298
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,080
and open a savings account.

299
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:29,450
[Anqing No.1 High School]

300
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:30,680
Comrade.

301
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,440
Comrade.

302
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,000
Who are you looking for?

303
00:09:33,070 --> 00:09:34,200
I'm looking for Chen Qing.

304
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,600
-Which Chen Qing?
-Yeah.

305
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,320
S-Senior class.

306
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,180
He's from Qijing Village.

307
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:40,960
Miss,

308
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:42,390
I brought you business.

309
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,630
Can you give me more of a discount?

310
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,750
The discount won't change.

311
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,670
But for old customers,

312
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:46,240
we'll give you

313
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,360
a free pair of pantyhose each.

314
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,030
How about that?

315
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,510
Sure, sure.

316
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:50,480
This is good stuff.

317
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,200
This is not bad.

318
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,630
I wore these before; they're comfortable.

319
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:53,690
Please come again.

320
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,050
Count them to make sure.

321
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,980
Come back soon.

322
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,870
How much is this coat?

323
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,390
The price is marked right there.

324
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,240
29.90.

325
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,390
For a piece of street junk like this,

326
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,030
the price is almost as high as

327
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,030
a department store's?

328
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,510
Only a fool would buy from you.

329
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:06,080
Why do you speak

330
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,960
so harshly?

331
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:07,720
Buy it if you want.

332
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,480
If not, just leave.

333
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:08,870
Exactly.

334
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:09,550
You're the owner

335
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:12,120
of the clothing store
across the street, right?

336
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,080
So you're a competitor.

337
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,720
Here to ruin my business, huh?

338
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,510
She really is.

339
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,910
She's the one selling clothes
across the street.

340
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,770
Are you sure you can buy her goods?

341
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,360
We don't know where she came from.

342
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,840
If there's any quality problem,

343
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,240
let's see if you can find her.

344
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,300
-That's true.
-No.

345
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,910
You look unfamiliar.

346
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:27,720
You won't be gone tomorrow, will you?

347
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,080
-Of course not.
-I don't think so.

348
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,610
I've never seen her before.

349
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,550
Don't even know where she

350
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,480
popped out from.

351
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:33,750
Dressed like that too.

352
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,670
Who knows if she's from

353
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,480
a decent family.

354
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,550
What nonsense are you talking about?

355
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,960
We are decent people.

356
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:39,600
Just because you say you're decent

357
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,320
doesn't mean you are.

358
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,030
Get lost!

359
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:42,480
Shut your trap!

360
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,440
Who are you?

361
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,360
You think this mother and daughter
are easy to bully,

362
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,960
don't you?

363
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,270
Listen to me.

364
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,320
Our Xiaolan

365
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,630
is not only beautiful

366
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:50,750
but also a top student.

367
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,630
She's about
to take the college entrance exam.

368
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,320
The principal of No.1 High School

369
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,080
personally came chasing after her.

370
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,080
And what we sell

371
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,870
are real fashionable goods.

372
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,510
No one wants

373
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:00,280
the trash

374
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,200
you sell.

375
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,390
What are you saying?

376
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,240
Let me tell you,

377
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,510
shut your mouth.

378
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:05,630
You look like a dirty rag.

379
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,480
No one wants you.

380
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,320
What are you saying?

381
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,580
I'm talking about you.

382
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,630
I'm talking about you.

383
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:10,670
Do you understand?

384
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,790
Excuse me. Excuse me.

385
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,120
None of you are good people.

386
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:13,890
Ladies,

387
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,840
stop arguing.

388
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:15,720
Who are you?

389
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,120
Mind your own business.

390
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,120
I'm Sun,

391
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:20,320
the principal of No.1 High School.

392
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,120
Xiaolan

393
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,720
is about to attend our school

394
00:11:22,730 --> 00:11:23,670
to take
the college entrance exam.

395
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:25,320
I must look after her.

396
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:28,360
You even hired performers?

397
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:29,960
He is Mr. Sun.

398
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,840
My niece goes to No.1 High School.

399
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,320
You must be Xia Xiaolan.

400
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,390
Yes.

401
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:36,080
You passed the placement exam

402
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,360
for No.1 High School.

403
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:42,050
Do you know

404
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,120
what score she got?

405
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,200
No idea.

406
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:46,360
446 points!

407
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:48,600
That exceeds

408
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,510
this year's
bachelor's degree cutoff.

409
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,030
And,

410
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,080
this child's exam paper

411
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,750
still has a lot of room for improvement.

412
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:54,670
If she revises well,

413
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:57,840
getting into a key university
next year won't be a problem.

414
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,440
Xiaolan,

415
00:11:58,810 --> 00:11:59,570
let's go

416
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,270
complete the enrollment procedures.

417
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:01,600
Okay.

418
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,030
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

419
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,320
But

420
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,550
can you let me sell these goods

421
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:07,240
first?

422
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:09,510
Xiaolan,

423
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,000
at a time like this,

424
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,030
you're still doing business here?

425
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:12,720
Mr. Sun,

426
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,080
I didn't know you would be coming today.

427
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,200
I waited at home for several days,

428
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,400
but there was no news.

429
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:18,840
Qi.

430
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:21,750
Hello, Xiaolan.

431
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:23,000
I am Ms. Qi,

432
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,390
who's responsible for grading your exam.

433
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,550
It's due to my mistake

434
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,670
that made you wait for so long.

435
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,600
I apologize.

436
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:28,120
No need.

437
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,510
Why don't we go to the school

438
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:31,270
to complete the procedures first?

439
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:31,930
How's that?

440
00:12:32,150 --> 00:12:33,670
Right. Let's handle the paperwork first.

441
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,730
This is important.

442
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,270
Fen.

443
00:12:35,290 --> 00:12:36,000
You go with her.

444
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,440
Right.

445
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,550
-I'll go with you.
-I'll stay here.

446
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:38,120
Let's go.

447
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:38,870
Go on. Hurry up.

448
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:39,360
Okay.

449
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:41,390
Come and take a look, everyone.

450
00:12:41,390 --> 00:12:43,000
Our goods are genuine.

451
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,130
Specially brought from Longcheng...

452
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,680
Thank you.

453
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,240
Thank you.

454
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,170
You're welcome.

455
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,150
Thank you both

456
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,410
for taking me seriously.

457
00:12:55,410 --> 00:12:56,690
You've seen

458
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,920
my family situation.

459
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:58,600
There's something

460
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,200
I'd like to discuss with you.

461
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:03,120
I will definitely
take the college entrance exam.

462
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,960
But I might not be able

463
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,720
to attend classes at school

464
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,630
this semester.

465
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,080
I would like to

466
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,880
settle my family affairs first.

467
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,650
Otherwise, even if I study,

468
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,080
I won't be able to focus.

469
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,160
But I promise,

470
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,750
I'll definitely return
to school next semester

471
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,950
and revise properly.

472
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,200
Xiaolan.

473
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,800
What are you saying?

474
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,200
I can support you.

475
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,240
Mom.

476
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,120
I know what I'm doing.

477
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,980
I can handle it.

478
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,720
Leave the stall to me.

479
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,200
I can learn slowly.

480
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,200
Trust me.

481
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:28,480
Didn't I pass the placement exam

482
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,680
through self-study?

483
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,880
Only new players make choices.

484
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,920
I've got a cheat code.

485
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,290
Of course, I want it all.

486
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,240
In this golden age,

487
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:40,240
whether studying or doing business,

488
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,720
I won't give up on either.

489
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:43,480
Xiaolan.

490
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,080
I think...

491
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,750
Mr. Sun.

492
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,970
I've made up my mind.

493
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:47,960
If No.1 High School

494
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,550
cannot accept my study plan,

495
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,150
I can ask at No.2 High School.

496
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:57,510
Fine.

497
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:59,960
As long as you're willing
to come to No.1 High School,

498
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,240
I agree to your terms.

499
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:03,320
Okay.

500
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:04,610
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

501
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,130
By the way, Xiaolan.

502
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,150
Keep your student ID and meal tickets

503
00:14:12,150 --> 00:14:13,120
safe.

504
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:14,650
Remember, every week,

505
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:16,640
you must report to school once.

506
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:18,270
You must take the monthly exams.

507
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:18,800
Xiaolan.

508
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,450
Study hard at home.

509
00:14:20,510 --> 00:14:21,440
Don't slack off.

510
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:23,050
I understand, Mr. Sun.

511
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:23,770
Good.

512
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:25,200
You may go home now.

513
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,960
Thank you, Sir.

514
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,960
Thank you, Ma'am.

515
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,490
Let's go.

516
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:37,650
Xiaolan, look.

517
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:39,750
Anqing No.1 High School Student ID.

518
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:41,150
Xia Xiaolan, Grade 12.

519
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,270
Three liang. Six liang.

520
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,260
Nine liang.

521
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,360
So much. I can't count it all.

522
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,200
Auntie,

523
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:49,950
I think I saw Xia Xiaolan.

524
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,960
Get back to work.

525
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,030
Your sister said,

526
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:58,840
when she comes back for New Year,

527
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,500
she'll settle it for herself.

528
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,000
Cheng.

529
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,200
Are you really going to repeat the year?

530
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,550
Just to chase a girl,

531
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:29,840
you're really going all out.

532
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,440
It's truly touching.

533
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:33,030
It isn't to impress her

534
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,240
that I'm repeating the year.

535
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,600
Her determination woke me up.

536
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,080
Look.

537
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:37,840
I've been back at school

538
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,700
for 2 weeks now.

539
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:40,390
I feel more and more that

540
00:15:40,390 --> 00:15:41,510
the decision to keep trying for college

541
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:42,440
is the right one.

542
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:45,060
Come with me to Xinhua Bookstore.

543
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:49,360
These are our usual

544
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,960
exercises and papers.

545
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:53,080
Mostly English ones.

546
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,360
Also, these are

547
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,080
the notes I took

548
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,120
in class myself.

549
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:05,840
I saw that you

550
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,170
missed so many classes.

551
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,670
And here are formulas

552
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:09,870
and things like that.

553
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,630
Some for physics and chemistry,

554
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,560
and English too.

555
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:15,120
Take this back.

556
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,680
I have my own study methods.

557
00:16:17,750 --> 00:16:19,410
I'll catch up on what I missed.

558
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:21,030
You need it more than I do.

559
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,120
But you missed so—

560
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,320
Don't you believe me?

561
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:25,890
If you don't believe me,

562
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,860
let's compare scores next month.

563
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,100
All right then.

564
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:34,150
Then you look at these,

565
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:36,000
and I'll take this back for myself.

566
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:36,910
Okay. Thanks.

567
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,390
I... I-I'll be going.

568
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,030
Chen Qing.

569
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,510
Ma'am.

570
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,050
You're leaving?

571
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:51,890
I-I'm off.

572
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:53,360
Not staying for dinner?

573
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,560
No, no, my mom cooked.

574
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:56,840
Xiaolan.

575
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,030
Why was that kid's face

576
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:00,120
all flushed red?

577
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:01,960
You know,

578
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,050
one time,

579
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,500
Chen Qing's mom told me...

580
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,310
-You...
-Auntie,

581
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,349
stop trying to set us up.

582
00:17:06,349 --> 00:17:07,480
I'm not interested.

583
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:08,960
Okay, okay.

584
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:10,930
Focus on your revision first.

585
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:11,510
In college,

586
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:13,170
there are plenty of good guys.

587
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:36,480
Chen Qing doesn't know my background.

588
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,280
The 1984 college entrance exam,

589
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,800
I'm determined to ace it.

590
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:42,480
Apart from my advantage in English,

591
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,000
I have another reason

592
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,330
why I must take the exam.

593
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,970
Because I liked math back then,

594
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:49,110
I solved every math paper

595
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:51,970
since the college entrance exams
were reinstated.

596
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:56,350
I got a very low score on one of them.

597
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,750
1984

598
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:04,960
National College Entrance Examination
math paper.

599
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,000
After struggling in this hell mode

600
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:31,880
for so long,

601
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:34,370
am I finally getting a cheat code?

602
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:37,200
If I can recall

603
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:38,510
the hellish

604
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,160
1984 college entrance exam

605
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,480
math paper

606
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,540
and get every question right,

607
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:45,000
then getting into college

608
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,400
won't be a problem at all.

609
00:18:49,390 --> 00:18:52,940
[Winter, 1983]

610
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:51,400
Ma'am!

611
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,200
It's you.

612
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,850
You're just in time.

613
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:56,960
Wait a moment.

614
00:19:00,830 --> 00:19:01,640
Just a second.

615
00:19:06,290 --> 00:19:06,900
This

616
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,320
was sent by the man

617
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:09,610
who came to eat noodles

618
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:10,810
with you last time.

619
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:12,730
He also wrote me a long letter,

620
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,960
telling me again and again

621
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:17,170
that I must pass these books to you.

622
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:17,870
By the way,

623
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:18,960
there is a letter for you too.

624
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:19,820
This is for you.

625
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:20,400
Okay.

626
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,790
What noodles do you want today?

627
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,410
Just a bowl of beef noodles.

628
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:24,350
Alright, wait a moment.

629
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:25,440
I'll go cook the noodles for you.

630
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:25,790
Okay.

631
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,680
Cook the noodles!

632
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:30,350
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

633
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:39,510
Hello, Comrade Xiaolan.

634
00:19:40,030 --> 00:19:41,160
The last telegram

635
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:42,640
caused you trouble,

636
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:43,950
so I didn't dare to rashly

637
00:19:43,950 --> 00:19:45,720
send the letter to the village this time.

638
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:48,320
I could only ask
the noodle shop owner for help.

639
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:50,350
Since we parted,

640
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:52,400
I have been
looking forward to your letter.

641
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,110
Meng! Meng!

642
00:19:53,110 --> 00:19:53,790
No!

643
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:55,050
Nothing for you today!

644
00:19:55,730 --> 00:19:57,460
I want to know how you are doing.

645
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,610
How is the business?

646
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,200
How are your studies?

647
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:03,210
I have also returned to the classroom.

648
00:20:03,210 --> 00:20:04,540
I am repeating the year,

649
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:07,910
preparing for next year's
college entrance exam.

650
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,170
Zhou Cheng!

651
00:20:11,070 --> 00:20:12,330
Let's play for a while.

652
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:13,480
You guys go ahead.

653
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:14,280
I'm revising.

654
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:14,960
Okay.

655
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,550
Last time I saw you only had textbooks

656
00:20:18,550 --> 00:20:19,880
among your study materials,

657
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,750
so I sent the revision materials I'm using

658
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:23,030
along with this letter.

659
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:25,070
I hope they'll be of help.

660
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:29,070
Study life is simple and boring,

661
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,110
but the thought

662
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:31,700
of you also working hard in Yunan

663
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:33,030
fills me with strength.

664
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,110
Winter in the capital is beautiful.

665
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,240
If there is a chance,

666
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,800
I really want to show you.

667
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:45,680
Finally, I hope your studies go well

668
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,360
and you stay healthy.

669
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:49,320
Looking forward to your reply.

670
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,680
Bro! Bro!

671
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:08,960
It's me! It's me!

672
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:10,000
It hurts...

673
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:13,070
That was so painful.

674
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,680
Why is there a novel?

675
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,590
Aren't you afraid
of affecting her studies?

676
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:22,000
This is called striking a balance
between work and rest.

677
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,440
With Xiaolan's intelligence,

678
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:25,220
getting into college is a sure thing.

679
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:26,080
But do you think

680
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:28,400
college is the only thing she's after?

681
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,220
What else is there?

682
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,920
The big wide world.

683
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:34,720
But Cheng,

684
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,200
the books you sent,

685
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:37,400
did she receive them?

686
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:38,480
Day in, day out,

687
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,480
you've practically emptied this library,

688
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,610
but you haven't even received a reply.

689
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:47,160
All right, all right.

690
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,030
Okay. My bad...

691
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,350
What is this?

692
00:21:52,650 --> 00:21:54,170
Shangdu City.

693
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,310
Xia Xiaolan?

694
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:57,960
Not bad.

695
00:21:58,550 --> 00:22:00,000
Sincerity pays off.

696
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:01,240
She got 1st place

697
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,680
in her exams.

698
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:03,690
First place?

699
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,270
For real? Let me see.

700
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,440
Who do you think you are?

701
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,160
Why so stingy?

702
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:11,750
I'm leaving.

703
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:12,400
Bro,

704
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:14,760
you should share the good stuff.

705
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:15,510
Sir, I'm back.

706
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:16,110
Happy New Year.

707
00:22:16,110 --> 00:22:16,840
You're back.

708
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:18,720
Coming through!

709
00:22:19,350 --> 00:22:20,210
Happy New Year.

710
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,110
Happy New Year.

711
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:21,970
Happy New Year.

712
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:23,650
Happy New Year.

713
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,350
Uncle Yong,

714
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,780
you struck it rich?

715
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,510
My dad wants you over for a drink.

716
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:29,550
I'll go in a couple of days.

717
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,160
Okay!

718
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:31,960
Dayong,

719
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:33,210
Happy New Year.

720
00:22:33,530 --> 00:22:34,000
By the way,

721
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,240
I heard Xiaolan

722
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,270
scored over 500.

723
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:38,110
College is in the bag, right?

724
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:39,870
She still needs to work hard.

725
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,000
Come on.

726
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:41,930
Quick, sit down.

727
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:43,350
Raise your glasses, everyone.

728
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:45,680
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

729
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:53,750
Happiness was sealed in the past.

730
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:56,640
Or perhaps it is right here.

731
00:22:57,920 --> 00:23:00,320
Even though there are many hardships here.

732
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:01,720
Poverty.

733
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,100
Backwardness.

734
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:04,440
And a beginning trapped in

735
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,830
a quagmire of rumors.

736
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:08,680
But it is also wonderful.

737
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:09,750
Because

738
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:11,940
I have a home again.

739
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:30,730
You're awake.

740
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,130
Morning, Mom!

741
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:32,880
Morning.

742
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,020
Happy New Year.

743
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:36,110
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

744
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:38,640
Xiaolan.

745
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:41,200
It's New Year's Day.

746
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,030
The whole family

747
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,640
is going to the fair together.

748
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,350
I was trying to talk your mom into it,

749
00:23:45,350 --> 00:23:46,550
but she refused to go.

750
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,760
I don't like crowded places.

751
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:50,350
It's the New Year.

752
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,400
It's nice to be somewhere lively.

753
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,200
You have to go.

754
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:54,340
Xiaolan, I'm leaving this to you.

755
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:55,310
Okay.

756
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:55,960
Hey!

757
00:23:56,990 --> 00:23:58,590
The Li family mentioned it yesterday.

758
00:23:58,590 --> 00:23:59,200
Do you know how much

759
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:00,200
a bowl of noodles there is?

760
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,030
6 dimes.

761
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,720
It was only 4 dimes last year.

762
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:04,000
Why join the crowd?

763
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:07,550
Mom, take this.

764
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:08,640
Hey!

765
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,850
What is this for?

766
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,110
It's not that you don't like

767
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:12,230
crowded places.

768
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,240
You just don't like going

769
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,700
to places that cost money.

770
00:24:16,370 --> 00:24:17,510
I can't take this money.

771
00:24:17,510 --> 00:24:18,480
It's hard-earned money. Take it.

772
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,200
Since it's hard-earned money,

773
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:20,720
if you save it up and don't spend it,

774
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,450
it'll just sit at home and mold.

775
00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:23,190
If you earn but don't spend,

776
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:24,720
isn't life just suffering?

777
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:25,800
Listen to me.

778
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:26,830
Don't save for me.

779
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:27,680
If you don't spend it all today,

780
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,610
don't come back.

781
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:30,720
Okay.

782
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,740
I'll listen to you.

783
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,400
Now that's right.

784
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:36,380
Hurry and wash your face.

785
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:37,240
I'll go tidy up.

786
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,030
Okay.

787
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:49,270
In the past, when Auntie took Cousin

788
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,500
to the amusement park,

789
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:52,160
I always said I didn't like it.

790
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,350
But how could that be true?

791
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:56,550
I was just a child back then.

792
00:24:58,110 --> 00:24:59,830
Living under someone else's roof,

793
00:24:59,830 --> 00:25:01,200
I was afraid of spending money

794
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:02,550
and causing trouble.

795
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,260
Living life again,

796
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,430
not only will I live happily,

797
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:08,440
but I also want my family and friends

798
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,370
to live happily.

799
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:23,870
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

800
00:25:23,890 --> 00:25:29,230
♪ Wipe away the glistening tears
in your eyes ♪

801
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,640
Lion dance!

802
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:33,960
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

803
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,590
How much is this?

804
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:40,250
♪ Take away all the sadness;
no matter who it is in the wind ♪

805
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:38,520
Look, there's popcorn over there.

806
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:39,910
I want popcorn

807
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:40,790
and rice crisps.

808
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:41,350
One bag of each.

809
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:41,950
All right.

810
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,920
It really feels like New Year.

811
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,720
There are sugar paintings here.

812
00:25:57,780 --> 00:25:58,540
I want one.

813
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:00,050
How much is this, Ma'am?

814
00:26:00,130 --> 00:26:00,860
2 dimes each.

815
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:01,430
Sure.

816
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:03,920
-Here.
-Okay.

817
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:04,830
Okay, come on. Spin it, miss.

818
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:05,290
Spin it.

819
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:07,030
A butterfly.

820
00:26:07,030 --> 00:26:07,690
Butterfly.

821
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:11,780
Fish! Fish!

822
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,280
Let's go look at the fish!

823
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:14,920
They're huge.

824
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:15,790
Come take a look.

825
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:16,680
Fish from Baixi Reservoir.

826
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,810
They're very fresh.

827
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:18,510
These big ones

828
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,160
are 15 each.

829
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,480
15 each?

830
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,740
That's too expensive.

831
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:22,880
It's not expensive. Buy it.

832
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,030
It's New Year. We'll take one.

833
00:26:24,030 --> 00:26:24,680
Such a big fish,

834
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,110
we can't cook like restaurants do.

835
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:27,770
It'd be a waste if we bought it.

836
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:29,390
Here, take it.

837
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:30,350
All right, all right.

838
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,350
Such an expensive

839
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,680
and huge fish!

840
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,440
Mrs. Chen.

841
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:34,590
Mrs. Chen, Happy New Year!

842
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:35,450
Happy New Year!

843
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,480
Happy New Year!

844
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:37,440
Everyone is out for a stroll?

845
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,070
Yes, yes.

846
00:26:38,070 --> 00:26:39,130
Let's go together.

847
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:40,510
Keep the biggest one for me.

848
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:41,510
Don't worry!

849
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,580
Jianhua, I'm getting hungry.

850
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,790
Go buy me a bun.

851
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,030
Wait for me here then.

852
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,360
Okay.

853
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:08,640
Ma'am,

854
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:09,440
I'd like a bun.

855
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:09,880
Sure.

856
00:27:10,650 --> 00:27:11,800
This one looks nice.

857
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:12,200
Here.

858
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:12,880
Try it.

859
00:27:13,270 --> 00:27:13,870
Tao, come.

860
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:14,900
Looks good.

861
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,360
What are you smiling at?

862
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,300
I saw you working in the fields

863
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,140
all day today.

864
00:27:43,480 --> 00:27:45,160
I filled a basin of water for you.

865
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,310
Wash up.

866
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:47,750
Thank you.

867
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,160
By the way,

868
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:55,220
there's a movie in the village today.

869
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,860
I'll go save a seat in a bit.

870
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,880
Otherwise, we won't get a good spot.

871
00:27:59,000 --> 00:27:59,350
Okay.

872
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,060
I'll change my clothes first.

873
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,200
I worked all day

874
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:02,960
and I stink.

875
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,590
I don't want to smell bad around you.

876
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:05,000
Okay.

877
00:28:12,580 --> 00:28:14,700
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

878
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:19,880
Jianhua.

879
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,330
Xiaolan, why did you...

880
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,400
Z-Ziyu.

881
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:27,330
Is something wrong?

882
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:52,750
This is delicious.

883
00:28:52,750 --> 00:28:53,400
Right?

884
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,240
Theirs is the best.

885
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,590
Come on, let's buy some too.

886
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:57,510
Buy some.

887
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:57,920
What?

888
00:28:59,110 --> 00:28:59,640
I'll pay. Let me get it.

889
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,240
No need, it's fine.

890
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:00,720
I'll buy it.

891
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,510
No, no.

892
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,590
Don't. You pay every time.

893
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:04,590
Ziyu.

894
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,350
Try it. Eat it while it's hot.

895
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:06,920
This child.

896
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,240
This kid is so pretty.

897
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:09,440
Say thank you.

898
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:12,280
How is it?

899
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:14,000
It's not good.

900
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,440
I won't eat it. You have it.

901
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:17,040
Weren't you hungry just now?

902
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:19,070
She's just like her mother.

903
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:24,830
Xiaolan.

904
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:26,310
Let's go look over there.

905
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,110
Right. Let's go.

906
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:28,640
Didn't we already go there?

907
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:31,450
Let's just look around here.
It's fine. Let's go.

908
00:29:31,790 --> 00:29:32,910
Ziyu, let's go.

909
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,410
Why leave? What's the big deal?

910
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:49,830
Xiaolan.

911
00:29:53,350 --> 00:29:54,350
It's New Year.

912
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:57,270
Since you insist on provoking me...

913
00:29:59,330 --> 00:30:00,040
Chen Qing.

914
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,880
Take Tao to play for a while.

915
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:03,350
Tao, let's go play.

916
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,470
Mom, come with me too.

917
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:06,590
I didn't bring money.

918
00:30:06,590 --> 00:30:07,000
I...

919
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,710
Xia Ziyu, why did you call me?

920
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:13,330
Except for an apology,

921
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:14,400
what else do you have

922
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,200
to say to me?

923
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,000
Apologize?

924
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,800
You should look like you mean it.

925
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:20,310
Who are you

926
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:21,570
pulling a long face at?

927
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:23,480
Auntie.

928
00:30:23,710 --> 00:30:24,570
Happy New Year.

929
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,160
Forget it. Forget it.

930
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:28,300
We dare not be the auntie
of a Golden Phoenix.

931
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:29,480
I don't have that luck.

932
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,740
Just say what you want.

933
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:32,110
Xiaolan.

934
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,030
Your sister didn't do anything

935
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:34,960
to wrong you.

936
00:30:35,490 --> 00:30:36,550
If there is a fault,

937
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,800
it is mine.

938
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,480
I chose

939
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,740
to be with your sister,

940
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,750
and I don't regret it at all.

941
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:44,730
Ziyu meant well.

942
00:30:45,230 --> 00:30:46,360
She wanted to say hi.

943
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:52,590
Don't look at my mother.

944
00:30:52,590 --> 00:30:53,440
My mother isn't

945
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:55,170
a pushover you can manipulate.

946
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:55,900
Xia Ziyu.

947
00:30:56,110 --> 00:30:57,640
What act are you putting on?

948
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:58,960
There is a stage right here.

949
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,190
Why don't you go up and act

950
00:31:00,190 --> 00:31:01,310
to perform for everyone?

951
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:02,680
Don't waste everyone's time at the market.

952
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:03,240
Right?

953
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:04,960
Xiaolan.

954
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:06,350
Jianhua is right.

955
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:08,270
I really just wanted to say hi to you

956
00:31:08,270 --> 00:31:08,930
and Auntie.

957
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:12,260
There is a misunderstanding between us.

958
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:13,400
But I hope

959
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:15,930
you won't take it out
on the rest of the family.

960
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:17,790
Can you go back and see Uncle?

961
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:20,240
He misses you and Auntie very much.

962
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,130
You have to think about Auntie.

963
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:25,240
Running back to her parents' home

964
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,480
is not the solution.

965
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:28,550
Wait a moment.

966
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,620
That's not the main point.

967
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:33,200
We aren't done with the business
between the three of us.

968
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:33,920
What's between the three of us

969
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:35,160
is not a misunderstanding.

970
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,110
Didn't Wang Jianhua

971
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:37,400
admit it for you?

972
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:39,880
He wronged me.

973
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,110
You stole my boyfriend.

974
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,440
Xia Ziyu.

975
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:45,110
Do you admit this or not?

976
00:31:45,110 --> 00:31:46,200
If you insist on putting it that way,

977
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,600
there is nothing I can do.

978
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,200
But regardless,

979
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:51,480
Uncle didn't do anything wrong.

980
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:52,550
As long as you agree

981
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,480
for Uncle and Auntie to reconcile,

982
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:56,170
I'm willing to do anything.

983
00:31:56,540 --> 00:31:58,030
You're really willing to do anything?

984
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:59,160
As long as I can do it.

985
00:32:00,850 --> 00:32:01,980
Then you really are

986
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:03,590
being too insincere.

987
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:06,070
You saw me a while ago.

988
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,510
You hesitated there for a long time,

989
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:08,350
and finally decided

990
00:32:08,350 --> 00:32:10,270
to come up and act out this sob story.

991
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:11,640
You just wanted to act generous

992
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,770
in front of your man.

993
00:32:13,070 --> 00:32:14,830
But you didn't expect me
to see through it.

994
00:32:14,830 --> 00:32:16,230
Now you're acting again,

995
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,200
trying to make others think

996
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,440
that my mother
ran back to her parents' home

997
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,900
because of her bad temper.

998
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:20,690
Xia Ziyu,

999
00:32:21,070 --> 00:32:22,440
is this really necessary?

1000
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:22,830
Xiaolan,

1001
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,560
I really didn't think that way.

1002
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:27,170
Did you really not think that way?

1003
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:28,820
Xia Ziyu.

1004
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:29,960
Do you know,

1005
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:31,990
if you want to be a villain,

1006
00:32:31,990 --> 00:32:33,510
there's no need to put up so much of an act.

1007
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:35,770
Otherwise, you'll be written out early.

1008
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:37,350
I originally just wanted

1009
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:37,920
to see

1010
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:39,450
what kind of person you are.

1011
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,160
But now,

1012
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,550
I'm sorry,

1013
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,330
you really disgust me.

1014
00:32:45,100 --> 00:32:45,830
Xia Xiaolan,

1015
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,160
don't go too far.

1016
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,030
What are you trying to do?

1017
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:49,630
Don't you lay a finger on her!

1018
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,130
That's Liu Fen.

1019
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:54,860
Liu Fen—

1020
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:55,550
Liu Yong?

1021
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:57,160
What are they doing?

1022
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,480
Bullying our girl?

1023
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,510
What are you doing?

1024
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:01,680
What are you doing?

1025
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,020
What are you doing?

1026
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:03,720
What are you doing?

1027
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,070
-What are you doing?
-What?

1028
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:05,830
What are you doing?

1029
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:06,720
You want to bully us, don't you?

1030
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:07,400
We didn't bully anyone!

1031
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,000
What do you want?

1032
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:08,720
You tell me.

1033
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:10,110
Ganging up to bully us.

1034
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,030
What do you mean?

1035
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:11,920
Who is bullying whom?

1036
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,250
There are so many of you.

1037
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:13,830
It's the New Year.

1038
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:14,480
What's going on here?

1039
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:15,160
Seriously.

1040
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,750
Can't we talk about this nicely?

1041
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:18,550
What's wrong, Comrade Xiaolan?

1042
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:20,830
Who are these two?

1043
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,880
Isn't that my "Golden Phoenix" cousin

1044
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,140
and my cousin-in-law?

1045
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:30,350
Xia Ziyu and Wang Jianhua?

1046
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:32,960
Xiaolan took good care of you, didn't she?

1047
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,890
Now you've found a new meal ticket?

1048
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:36,270
By the way,

1049
00:33:36,270 --> 00:33:37,070
Wang Jianhua,

1050
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:40,270
your round-trip travel expenses,

1051
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:42,110
food and boarding expenses,
and transport costs back then,

1052
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:43,400
I paid for all of that, didn't I?

1053
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,800
Then you suddenly told me

1054
00:33:44,830 --> 00:33:46,490
you wanted to be with Xia Ziyu.

1055
00:33:46,490 --> 00:33:47,200
In that case,

1056
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,660
pay me back my money first.

1057
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:50,450
I've calculated it for you.

1058
00:33:50,450 --> 00:33:51,970
It's 35 yuan in total.

1059
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:52,920
I rounded it down.

1060
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,960
I'm not taking advantage of you.

1061
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:54,440
Pay up.

1062
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:55,110
What's going on?

1063
00:33:55,110 --> 00:33:56,000
Take it out.

1064
00:33:56,030 --> 00:33:56,760
Is that true?

1065
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:58,200
What's going on?

1066
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,480
Wh-What's going on?

1067
00:34:04,430 --> 00:34:05,560
Wh-What's going on?

1068
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:22,440
Here!

1069
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:23,500
What are you doing?

1070
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,600
Give it to her!

1071
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,440
Xia Xiaolan.

1072
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:28,150
If insulting me like this

1073
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:29,550
is what it takes for you to cool off,

1074
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:31,219
I'll pay the money for Jianhua.

1075
00:34:31,219 --> 00:34:33,199
Xia Ziyu, you're so generous.

1076
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,800
That 35 yuan

1077
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,360
took me years to save.

1078
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,440
But you?

1079
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,920
The whole family supports just you.

1080
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:41,000
You took out

1081
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,000
this 35 yuan

1082
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:42,760
so easily.

1083
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,360
I don't want what's extra.

1084
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:48,020
Have fun supporting your man.

1085
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:49,830
W-Watch your mouth.

1086
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,520
Let's go.

1087
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:55,960
Hurry up.

1088
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:57,760
Serves you right.

1089
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:58,360
Show's over!

1090
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,110
Show's over!

1091
00:34:59,590 --> 00:35:01,280
So annoying.

1092
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:03,080
Now we have money to buy fish.

1093
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,150
Mom,

1094
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,600
let me introduce you.

1095
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,510
This is Zhou Cheng,

1096
00:35:06,510 --> 00:35:07,920
the person who helped me before.

1097
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,590
Hello, Ma'am.

1098
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:09,360
Zhou Cheng,

1099
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:10,320
thank you for helping Xiaolan.

1100
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,190
Not at all. It was the right thing to do.

1101
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:12,280
You saved the day today.

1102
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,070
Let's go. I'm treating you to a meal.

1103
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:13,440
Yeah, yeah.

1104
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:13,880
What do you want to eat?

1105
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,190
Let's go.

1106
00:35:14,190 --> 00:35:15,520
Let's go eat at our home.

1107
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,280
Happy New Year!

1108
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,300
Happy New Year!

1109
00:35:23,510 --> 00:35:26,110
We're home.

1110
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:28,000
Thank you.

1111
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:28,840
Slow down.

1112
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,860
Come here, let me hold you.

1113
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:31,850
Let's go.

1114
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,190
Let's go.

1115
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:34,510
Thanks.

1116
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,360
Happy New Year!

1117
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,290
Dayong, Dayong.

1118
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,730
You have guests?

1119
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,590
Fengmei's relatives.

1120
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:43,110
Right.

1121
00:35:43,230 --> 00:35:44,400
My nephew.

1122
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,110
No wonder I haven't seen him before.

1123
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:46,900
It's for me?

1124
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:49,400
What are you doing?

1125
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:51,150
It's for my father-in-law.

1126
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:52,510
See you later.

1127
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:53,130
See you.

1128
00:36:13,070 --> 00:36:13,630
Xiaolan.

1129
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:15,320
What are you making?

1130
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,670
One fish, four ways to eat.

1131
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:19,110
Watch and learn.

1132
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:25,160
I've never had it like this.

1133
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,000
Try some later.

1134
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,000
It's really good.

1135
00:36:35,260 --> 00:36:35,760
Let me do it, Auntie.

1136
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,440
No need, Zhou.

1137
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,190
Go to the kitchen.

1138
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,400
Help Xiaolan.

1139
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,150
Okay.

1140
00:36:44,690 --> 00:36:45,280
This young man

1141
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:47,280
is really handsome.

1142
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,670
Xiaolan is pretty too.

1143
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,440
It smells so good.

1144
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:53,950
Not bad, Xiaolan.

1145
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:57,320
Don't just stand there.
Peel some garlic for me.

1146
00:36:58,680 --> 00:36:59,520
Look at him,

1147
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:01,230
coming to our house during the New Year.

1148
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:02,400
Is he interested

1149
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,060
in our Xiaolan?

1150
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:04,330
He is definitely interested.

1151
00:37:04,330 --> 00:37:05,660
He confessed directly.

1152
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,880
He wants to pursue Xiaolan

1153
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,630
and date her.

1154
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,560
But Xiaolan refused.

1155
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:12,900
She was very clear.

1156
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,410
Studies come first.

1157
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,670
She doesn't want anything else.

1158
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:17,200
But the kid hasn't given up.

1159
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:22,030
Coming!

1160
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,260
One fish, four ways to eat.

1161
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:26,280
Dinner is served!

1162
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:26,880
Let's eat!

1163
00:37:27,550 --> 00:37:29,320
I want that fish ball.

1164
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,880
Look at you, so impatient.

1165
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:32,110
We have a guest today.

1166
00:37:32,410 --> 00:37:33,440
He hasn't eaten yet.

1167
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:34,640
It's okay. Here, Tao.

1168
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:35,510
Here.

1169
00:37:36,370 --> 00:37:36,770
Look.

1170
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:37,760
Thank you!

1171
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,710
Let's have a toast first.

1172
00:37:39,710 --> 00:37:40,280
Right. Come on.

1173
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,320
Xiaolan is amazing.

1174
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,480
She made all this.

1175
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:42,840
Come on.

1176
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,120
Welcome, Zhou.

1177
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:44,710
Great.

1178
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:45,960
-Cheers.
-Thank you.

1179
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:49,960
Zhou.

1180
00:37:50,990 --> 00:37:53,450
Still delivering goods
during the New Year?

1181
00:37:54,190 --> 00:37:55,630
I don't deliver goods anymore.

1182
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:56,690
Just like Xiaolan,

1183
00:37:56,890 --> 00:37:57,800
I'm repeating the year

1184
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:00,190
preparing for next year's
college entrance exams.

1185
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,720
You're taking the exam too?

1186
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:06,760
We are basically

1187
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:08,490
long-distance study buddies.

1188
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:09,940
What does that mean?

1189
00:38:09,940 --> 00:38:10,600
What buddy?

1190
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:11,660
Long-distance.

1191
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:13,080
It means two different places.

1192
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,520
He sent me

1193
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:16,400
a lot of study materials recently.

1194
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,030
It's been very helpful.

1195
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:18,960
Besides,

1196
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:20,320
he helped us

1197
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,320
with the situation today.

1198
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:22,360
So inviting him to dinner

1199
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,690
is the least we could do.

1200
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,680
That's right.

1201
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,320
Thank you, Zhou.

1202
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,360
Welcome. Come on.

1203
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:26,840
You're welcome, Ma'am.

1204
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,700
Have some fish.

1205
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:29,400
Thank you, Ma'am.

1206
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:30,000
I'll help myself.

1207
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:30,460
This...

1208
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:31,800
Zhou, have some fish.

1209
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,400
He can help himself.

1210
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,590
He's a big young man.

1211
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:36,180
We are classmates now.

1212
00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:36,960
We help each other.

1213
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:37,360
Right.

1214
00:38:37,590 --> 00:38:37,880
Good.

1215
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,670
Helping each other
and making progress together.

1216
00:38:39,670 --> 00:38:40,870
What a perfect match.

1217
00:38:44,990 --> 00:38:46,100
I... I mean

1218
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:48,630
a perfect match as study partners.

1219
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:49,610
Look at them.

1220
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,400
Learning from each other.

1221
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,800
Eat up, eat up.

1222
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:52,800
I...

1223
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:53,960
Here, Fengmei.

1224
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,760
Auntie, have some vegetables.

1225
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,360
Okay.

1226
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:57,480
I'll eat.

1227
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,670
Zhou Cheng.

1228
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:03,590
You're still staying at that guesthouse,

1229
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:04,030
right?

1230
00:39:04,160 --> 00:39:05,110
Yes, I'm still staying there.

1231
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:06,400
I'll take you back

1232
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,330
on my bike later.

1233
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:08,800
Okay.

1234
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,340
Thank you, Sir.

1235
00:39:11,920 --> 00:39:13,320
Come on, have a drink.

1236
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:14,770
Cheers.

1237
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:15,280
Sir.

1238
00:39:21,670 --> 00:39:22,630
Pour it.

1239
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,210
What did you say?

1240
00:39:25,030 --> 00:39:27,320
That's 35 yuan,

1241
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,780
and you just gave it to her?

1242
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:32,560
Grandma, it's my fault.

1243
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:34,550
I didn't protect Ziyu well.

1244
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:35,360
Jianhua.

1245
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,920
It's not your fault.

1246
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,320
I don't blame Xiaolan either.

1247
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:39,650
That's just her temper.

1248
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:40,880
I'm used to it.

1249
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:43,170
You're used to it, but I'm not.

1250
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,510
She's out of control.

1251
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,850
We must get that money back.

1252
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,840
I thought going to school

1253
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:51,110
would make her better.

1254
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:51,770
Who knew

1255
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,960
she's still an ungrateful wretch.

1256
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:55,590
I'm furious.

1257
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:00,710
Mother.

1258
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:02,880
It's the New Year.

1259
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,140
Don't get so worked up.

1260
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:06,030
Look, it's the New Year.

1261
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:08,430
Our Ziyu...

1262
00:40:08,670 --> 00:40:10,400
You watched her grow up.

1263
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:12,370
You know

1264
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:13,660
her temperament best.

1265
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:15,880
Honest, kind,

1266
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,250
and good-hearted.

1267
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:18,970
Doesn't she take after you?

1268
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:21,550
She always thinks of the family.

1269
00:40:23,150 --> 00:40:23,810
You know...

1270
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,760
Mother, don't blame me.

1271
00:40:25,760 --> 00:40:27,960
I shouldn't be doing this on New Year...

1272
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:29,630
You guys go ahead and eat.

1273
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:30,960
I really can't bear

1274
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:32,030
to see Second Uncle and Second Aunt

1275
00:40:32,030 --> 00:40:33,160
fighting like this.

1276
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:34,720
Second Uncle.

1277
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:35,710
You and Second Aunt

1278
00:40:35,710 --> 00:40:37,400
haven't seen each other for so long.

1279
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:39,530
There must be some misunderstanding.

1280
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,070
Grandma.

1281
00:40:45,710 --> 00:40:47,190
Xiaolan is still a Xia.

1282
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:49,430
Second Uncle.

1283
00:40:49,570 --> 00:40:50,770
Xiaolan is stubborn.

1284
00:40:50,970 --> 00:40:51,960
If she could come back,

1285
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:53,280
it would be better than anything.

1286
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,360
Please don't mention

1287
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:56,020
anything about apologizing.

1288
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,880
She is studying at No.1 High School now.

1289
00:40:57,880 --> 00:40:58,670
If Second Uncle and Second Aunt

1290
00:40:58,670 --> 00:41:00,070
could get back together,

1291
00:41:00,510 --> 00:41:02,170
Xiaolan could study in peace.

1292
00:41:02,620 --> 00:41:04,880
She's staying with her maternal uncle,
after all.

1293
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,480
That's living under someone else's roof.

1294
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,410
How could she focus on her studies?

1295
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:10,960
Her life must be difficult.

1296
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:37,540
Zhou Cheng.

1297
00:41:38,590 --> 00:41:39,000
Uncle.

1298
00:41:39,290 --> 00:41:40,400
The rain is so heavy.

1299
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:41,800
How are you getting back?

1300
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,070
Yeah.

1301
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:46,370
It really is coming down hard.

1302
00:41:47,320 --> 00:41:48,450
If you can't go back,

1303
00:41:49,100 --> 00:41:50,430
stay with Tao and me

1304
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:51,210
tonight.

1305
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:52,160
Don't go back.

1306
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:54,280
Xiaolan,

1307
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:56,520
can your aunt sleep with you?

1308
00:41:57,230 --> 00:41:57,670
Sure.

1309
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:00,000
Fengmei!

1310
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:02,540
Zhou Cheng is staying here tonight!

1311
00:42:02,540 --> 00:42:03,600
Get an extra quilt!

1312
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:04,600
All right!

1313
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,620
Thank you, Sir.

1314
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:11,760
Are you happy?

1315
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:16,610
Let me do it. Let me.

1316
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:35,690
Have some water.

1317
00:42:35,710 --> 00:42:36,770
Careful, it's hot.

1318
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:42,970
I'm sorry you had to suffer

1319
00:42:43,230 --> 00:42:44,360
through this today.

1320
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:46,670
Jianhua,

1321
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,940
please don't think like that.

1322
00:42:49,070 --> 00:42:49,760
Actually, I think

1323
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:51,160
it turned out fine today.

1324
00:42:51,670 --> 00:42:53,190
You returned the money to her.

1325
00:42:53,190 --> 00:42:54,800
From now on, you don't owe her anything.
